On December 22, 2015, Pieterse became engaged to her long-term boyfriend Hudson Sheaffer.<ref>{{cite web |last=Murphy |first=Shaunna |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2716863/sasha-pieterse-pretty-little-liars-engaged/ |title='Pretty Little Liars' Star Sasha Pieterse Is Engaged: See The Romantic Pics |work=[[MTV News]] |publisher=[[Viacom (2005‚Äìpresent)|Viacom]] |date=December 23, 2015 |access-date=December 26, 2015 |archive-date=May 7, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507011051/http://www.mtv.com/news/2716863/sasha-pieterse-pretty-little-liars-engaged/ |url-status=dead }}</ref> They were married on May 27, 2018, at [[Castle Leslie]] in [[Glaslough|Glaslough, Ireland]].<ref>{{cite web|last=Corriston|first=Michele|title=Pretty Little Liars Star Sasha Pieterse Marries Hudson Sheaffer at Irish Castle|url=https://people.com/tv/sasha-pieterse-marries-hudson-sheaffer/|website=People|access-date=May 27, 2018|date=May 27, 2018|archive-date=May 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528020351/https://people.com/tv/sasha-pieterse-marries-hudson-sheaffer/|url-status=live}}</ref> On May 27, 2020, Pieterse announced that she and Sheaffer were expecting their first child.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sasha Pieterse Expecting First Child with Husband Hudson Sheaffer: 'We Are So Excited'|url=https://people.com/parents/sasha-pieterse-pregnant-expecting-first-child-hudson-sheaffer/|website=PEOPLE.com|date=May 27, 2020|last=Merrett|first=Robyn|language=EN|access-date=May 27, 2020|archive-date=November 16, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116222521/https://people.com/parents/sasha-pieterse-pregnant-expecting-first-child-hudson-sheaffer/|url-status=live}}</ref> Their son was born in November 2020.<ref>{{cite magazine|last1=VanHoose|first1=Benjamin|last2=McGovern|first2=Tim|date=November 13, 2020|title=Sasha Pieterse and Husband Hudson Sheaffer Welcome Their First Child: 'We Are Absolutely in Love with Him'|url=https://people.com/parents/sasha-pieterse-welcomes-first-child-baby-son-husband-hudson-sheaffer/|magazine=People|access-date=November 14, 2020|archive-date=November 14, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114022613/https://people.com/parents/sasha-pieterse-welcomes-first-child-baby-son-husband-hudson-sheaffer/|url-status=live}}</ref> As of 2022, the family resides in Nashville, Tennessee.<ref>{{cite web |last=Dodson |first=P. Claire |url=https://www.teenvogue.com/story/pretty-little-liars-star-sasha-pieterse-original-sin-emison-interview |title='"Pretty Little Liars" Star Sasha Pieterse Talks "Original Sin," Emison, and Advice for Spinoff Cast |work=[[Teen Vogue]] |publisher=[[Teen Vogue|Conde Nast]] |date=July 28, 2022 |access-date=July 31, 2022 |archive-date=July 28, 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220728133316/https://www.teenvogue.com/story/pretty-little-liars-star-sasha-pieterse-original-sin-emison-interview |url-status=live }}</ref>

